Package boundary.menu

Interface ManagerMenu

All Superinterfaces:
CommonMenu
All Known Implementing Classes:
ManagerUI
public interface ManagerMenu extends CommonMenu
Interface for manager menu options in the BTO system. Managers can manage projects, officers, applications, and enquiries.
